name: active_cycles_pm
long_description: Number of cycles a multiprocessor has at least one active warp.

name: active_warps_pm
long_description: Accumulated number of active warps per cycle. For every cycle it increments by the number of active warps in the cycle which can be in the range 0 to 64.

name: shared_ld_transactions
long_description: Number of transactions for shared load accesses. Maximum transaction size in volta is 128 bytes, any warp accessing more than 128 bytes will cause multiple transactions for a shared load instruction. This also includes extra transactions caused by shared bank conflicts.

name: shared_st_transactions
long_description: Number of transactions for shared store accesses. Maximum transaction size in volta is 128 bytes, any warp accessing more than 128 bytes will cause multiple transactions for a shared store instruction. This also includes extra transactions caused by shared bank conflicts.

name: elapsed_cycles_sm
long_description: elapsed clocks

name: elapsed_cycles_pm
long_description: elapsed clocks on SM

name: inst_executed_fp16_pipe_s0
long_description: Number of warp instructions executed by fp16 pipe on SM sub-partition 0.

name: inst_executed_fp16_pipe_s1
long_description: Number of warp instructions executed by fp16 pipe on SM sub-partition 1

name: inst_executed_fp16_pipe_s2
long_description: Number of warp instructions executed by fp16 pipe on SM sub-partition 2

name: inst_executed_fp16_pipe_s3
long_description: Number of warp instructions executed by fp16 pipe on SM sub-partition 3

name: inst_executed_fp64_pipe_s0
long_description: Number of warp instructions executed by fp64 pipe on SM sub-partition 0

name: inst_executed_fp64_pipe_s1
long_description: Number of warp instructions executed by fp64 pipe on SM sub-partition 1

name: inst_executed_fp64_pipe_s2
long_description: Number of warp instructions executed by fp64 pipe on SM sub-partition 2

name: inst_executed_fp64_pipe_s3
long_description: Number of warp instructions executed by fp64 pipe on SM sub-partition 3

name: inst_executed_fma_pipe_s0
long_description: Number of warp instructions executed by fma pipe on SM sub-partition 0

name: inst_executed_fma_pipe_s1
long_description: Number of warp instructions executed by fma pipe on SM sub-partition 1

name: inst_executed_fma_pipe_s2
long_description: Number of warp instructions executed by fma pipe on SM sub-partition 2

name: inst_executed_fma_pipe_s3
long_description: Number of warp instructions executed by fma pipe on SM sub-partition 3

name: shared_ld_bank_conflict
long_description: Number of shared load bank conflict generated when the addresses for two or more shared memory load requests fall in the same memory bank.

name: shared_st_bank_conflict
long_description: Number of shared store bank conflict generated when the addresses for two or more shared memory store requests fall in the same memory bank.

name: tensor_pipe_active_cycles_s0
long_description: Number of cycles where tensor pipe was active on  SM sub-partition 0

name: tensor_pipe_active_cycles_s1
long_description: Number of cycles where tensor pipe was active on  SM sub-partition 1

name: tensor_pipe_active_cycles_s2
long_description: Number of cycles where tensor pipe was active on  SM sub-partition 2

name: tensor_pipe_active_cycles_s3
long_description: Number of cycles where tensor pipe was active on  SM sub-partition 3

name: fb_subp0_read_sectors
long_description: Number of DRAM read requests to sub partition 0, increments by 1 for 32 byte access.

name: fb_subp1_read_sectors
long_description: Number of DRAM read requests to sub partition 1, increments by 1 for 32 byte access.

name: fb_subp0_write_sectors
long_description: Number of DRAM write requests to sub partition 0, increments by 1 for 32 byte access.

name: fb_subp1_write_sectors
long_description: Number of DRAM write requests to sub partition 1, increments by 1 for 32 byte access.

name: active_cycles
long_description: Number of cycles a multiprocessor has at least one active warp

name: active_warps
long_description: Accumulated number of active warps per cycle. For every cycle it increments by the number of active warps in the cycle which can be in the range 0 to 64.

name: prof_trigger_00
long_description: Number of pmtrig instructions executed where Imm16 & 0x0001

name: prof_trigger_01
long_description: Number of pmtrig instructions executed where Imm16 & 0x0002

name: prof_trigger_02
long_description: Number of pmtrig instructions executed where Imm16 & 0x0004

name: prof_trigger_03
long_description: Number of pmtrig instructions executed where Imm16 & 0x0008

name: prof_trigger_04
long_description: Number of pmtrig instructions executed where Imm16 & 0x0010

name: prof_trigger_05
long_description: Number of pmtrig instructions executed where Imm16 & 0x0020

name: prof_trigger_06
long_description: Number of pmtrig instructions executed where Imm16 & 0x0040

name: prof_trigger_07
long_description: Number of pmtrig instructions executed where Imm16 & 0x0080

name: inst_issued0
long_description: Number of cycles that did not issue any instruction, increments per warp.

name: inst_issued1
long_description: Number of cycles that issued single instruction, increments per warp.

name: inst_executed
long_description: Number of instructions executed per warp.

name: thread_inst_executed
long_description: Number of instructions executed by the active threads. For each instruction it increments by number of threads, including predicated-off threads, that execute the instruction. It does not include replays.

name: not_predicated_off_thread_inst_executed
short_description: Not predicated off thread instruction executed
long_description: Number of instructions executed by the active and not predicated off threads. For each instruction it increments by number of active and non-predicated off threads that execute the instruction. It does not include replays.

name: generic_load
long_description: Number of LD instructions executed

name: generic_store
long_description: Number of ST instructions executed

name: atom_count
long_description: Number of ATOM instructions executed

name: global_atom_cas
long_description: Number of ATOM.CAS instructions executed

name: gred_count
long_description: Number of RED instructions executed

name: global_load
long_description: Number of LDG instructions executed

name: global_store
long_description: Number of STG instructions executed

name: local_load
long_description: Number of LDL instructions executed

name: local_store
long_description: Number of STL instructions executed

name: shared_atom
long_description: Number of shared ATOMS instructions executed

name: shared_atom_cas
long_description: Number of shared ATOMS.CAS instructions executed

name: shared_load
long_description: Number of LDS instructions executed

name: shared_store
long_description: Number of STS instructions executed

name: warps_launched
long_description: Number of warps launched

name: sm_cta_launched
long_description: Number of ctas launched

name: l2_subp0_write_sector_misses
long_description: Number of write requests sent to DRAM from slice 0 of L2 cache. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp1_write_sector_misses
long_description: Number of write requests sent to DRAM from slice 1 of L2 cache. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp0_read_sector_misses
long_description: Number of read requests sent to DRAM from slice 0 of L2 cache. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp1_read_sector_misses
long_description: Number of read requests sent to DRAM from slice 1 of L2 cache. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp0_read_tex_sector_queries
short_description: l2 subp0 read tex sector queries
long_description: Number of read requests from Texture cache to slice 0 of L2 cache. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp0_write_tex_sector_queries
short_description: l2 subp0 write tex sector queries
long_description: Number of write requests from Texture cache to slice 0 of L2 cache. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp0_read_tex_hit_sectors
short_description: l2 subp0 read tex hit sectors
long_description: Number of read requests from Texture cache that hit in slice 0 of L2 cache. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp0_write_tex_hit_sectors
short_description: l2 subp0 write tex hit sectors
long_description: Number of write requests from Texture cache that hit in slice 0 of L2 cache. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp0_read_sysmem_sector_queries
long_description: Number of system memory read requests to slice 0 of L2 cache. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp0_write_sysmem_sector_queries
long_description: Number of system memory write requests to slice 0 of L2 cache. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp0_total_read_sector_queries
long_description: Total read requests to slice 0 of L2 cache. This includes requests from  L1, Texture cache, system memory. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp0_total_write_sector_queries
long_description: Total write requests to slice 0 of L2 cache. This includes requests from  L1, Texture cache, system memory. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp1_read_tex_sector_queries
short_description: l2 subp1 read tex sector queries
long_description: Number of read requests from Texture cache to slice 1 of L2 cache. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp1_write_tex_sector_queries
short_description: l2 subp1 write tex sector queries
long_description: Number of write requests from Texture cache to slice 1 of L2 cache. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp1_read_tex_hit_sectors
short_description: l2 subp1 read tex hit sectors
long_description: Number of read requests from Texture cache that hit in slice 1 of L2 cache. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp1_write_tex_hit_sectors
short_description: l2 subp1 write tex hit sectors
long_description: Number of write requests from Texture cache that hit in slice 1 of L2 cache. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp1_read_sysmem_sector_queries
long_description: Number of system memory read requests to slice 1 of L2 cache. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp1_write_sysmem_sector_queries
long_description: Number of system memory write requests to slice 1 of L2 cache. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp1_total_read_sector_queries
long_description: Total read requests to slice 1 of L2 cache. This includes requests from  L1, Texture cache, system memory. This increments by 1 for each 32-byte access.

name: l2_subp1_total_write_sector_queries

name: pcie_tx_active_pulse
long_description: Number of pulses for which data transmission through PCIe was active.

name: pcie_rx_active_pulse
long_description: Number of pulses for which data receive through PCIe was active.
